<h1 class="mb-5 text-4xl font-bold">About</h1>

<h4 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-bold">Share your ideas with the world and find others.</h4>

<p class="mb-3">
  Ideator is an idea-sharing platform built to spark creativity and collaboration. Whether you’re a thinker, innovator, or simply someone with a great concept to share—you’re welcome here.
</p>

<p class="mb-3">
  At its core, Ideator encourages users to:
  <ul>
    <li>Share ideas with the world in a simple and engaging format.</li>
    <li>Explore ideas from a diverse community of thinkers and creators.</li>
    <li>Collaborate and provide feedback to help ideas grow and evolve.</li>
  </ul>
</p>

<p class="mb-3">
  We believe great ideas flourish when they are shared. Some ideas may become startups, some may shape communities, and some might simply spark joy or curiosity. Ideator exists to support every step of that journey.
</p>
